title: KandyPens Oura Atomizer
description: ABOUT THE KANDYPENS OURA ATOMIZER The KandyPens Oura Atomizer comes with a quartz crystal bucket that is heated by a nichrome oil. The quartz bucket reaches temperature quickly and has fantastic heat retention for large sessions. This is an original equipment manufacturer product designed to be a replacement atomizer for the KandyPens Oura Vaporizer.     WHAT'S IN THE BOX  1x KandyPens Oura Atomizer
